feat(api): webhook dispatch system and enhanced rate limiting (#75, #76)

Webhook system (closes #75):
- 8 typed event definitions (credit.issued/retired/transferred,
  attestation.verified, marketplace.order.filled, contract.settled,
  trigger.fired, bridge.status_changed)
- ML-DSA-87 signed payloads with X-SC-Signature header
- Webhook endpoint CRUD routes (POST/GET/DELETE /webhooks)
- Dispatch engine with exponential backoff retry (max 5 attempts, 10s timeout)
- Delivery log tracking with per-webhook history endpoint

Rate limiting & pagination (closes #76):
- Sliding window algorithm replacing simple counter
- Per-tier rate limits (public:20, buyer:50, auditor:100, owner:200 req/s)
- X-RateLimit-Limit/Remaining/Reset headers + 429 with Retry-After
- page_size parameter with validation (min 1, max 100, default 25)
- page_size included in pagination response metadata
